Properties.Caption: Просмотр безденежного финансирования - расходы
Properties.Tag: Select [K_BD].[CBD] As [Код бюджета], [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [DOC].[DDOC] As [Дата документа], [DOC_ZF_R].[DBN] As [Дата проводки], [K_UL_K_UL].[CUL_PARENT] As [Распорядитель], [K_UL].[CUL] As [Организация], [DOC_ZF_R].[CDOC] As [Поручение], [DOC_ZF_R].[DDOC] As [Дата поручения], Sum([ZF_R].[SUMM]) As [Сумма] From (((((((((([DOC] With (NoLock) Inner Join [Apps_Groups] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[Apps_GroupsID]=[Apps_Groups].[Apps_GroupsID])) Inner Join [DOC_DOC] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[DOCID]=[DOC_DOC].[DOCID] And [DOC].[K_TDID]=[DOC_DOC].[K_TDID])) Inner Join [DOC] As [DOC_ZF_R] With (NoLock) On ([DOC_DOC].[DOCID_PARENT]=[DOC_ZF_R].[DOCID] And [DOC_DOC].[K_TDID_PARENT]=[DOC_ZF_R].[K_TDID])) Inner Join [ZF_R] With (NoLock) On ([DOC_ZF_R].[DOCID]=[ZF_R].[DOCID])) Inner Join [K_LSR] With (NoLock) On ([ZF_R].[K_LSRID]=[K_LSR].[K_LSRID])) Inner Join [K_OT] With (NoLock) On ([K_LSR].[K_OTID]=[K_OT].[K_OTID])) Inner Join [K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([ZF_R].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Left Join [K_LS] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_LSID]=[K_LS].[K_LSID])) Left Join [K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_ULID]=[K_UL].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_BD] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_BDID]=[K_BD].[K_BDID])) Where [DOC].[K_TDID]=56 And |0 Group by [K_BD].[CBD], [DOC].[CDOC], [DOC].[DDOC], [DOC_ZF_R].[DBN], [K_UL_K_UL].[CUL_PARENT], [K_UL].[CUL], [DOC_ZF_R].[CDOC], [DOC_ZF_R].[DDOC] Order by |1
